\c 3
\p
\v 1 Zvino takatendeuka ndokukwira nenzira yeBhashani. Ogi mambo weBhashani ndokubudira kusangana nesu, iye nevanhu vake vese\x + Num. 21.33. Det. 29.7.\x*, kuzorwa paEdhirei\x + 3.10. Det. 1.4.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino Jehovha wakati kwandiri: Usamutya, nokuti ndichamupa iye nevanhu vake vese nenyika yake muruoko rwako. Zvino uchamuitira sezvawakaita kuna Sihoni mambo weVaAmori waigara paHeshibhoni\x + Num. 21.24,34.\x*.
\v 3 Naizvozvo Jehovha Mwari wedu wakapa muruoko rwedu Ogiwo mambo weBhashani, nevanhu vake vese; tikamurova kusvika pasina waakasiirwa wakasara\x + Num. 21.33,35.\x*.
\v 4 Zvino takatapa maguta ake ese nenguva iyo; hakuna kuva neguta ratisina kutora kwavari, maguta makumi matanhatu, dunhu rose reArigobhu, ushe hwaOgi muBhashani\x + 3.13,14. 1 Madz. 4.13.\x*.
\v 5 Awa maguta ese aiva akashoshewa nemasvingo marefu, masuwo, nemazariro; kunze kwemisha mizhinji-zhinji yaiva isina masvingo\x + 1 Zvak. 6.18. Esi. 9.19.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino takaaparadza chose\x + 7.2.\x*, sezvatakaita kuna Sihoni mambo weHeshibhoni\x + 2.24. Num. 32.37.\x*, takaparadza chose maguta ese, varume, vakadzi, nevanana\x + 2.34.\x*.
\v 7 Asi zvipfuwo zvose nezvakapambiwa zvemaguta takazvitapira.
\v 8 Zvino nenguva iyo takatora nyika paruoko rwemadzimambo maviri eVaAmori aiva mhiri kwaJoridhani, kubva parwizi Arinoni kusvika pagomo reHerimoni.
\v 9 (Herimoni\x + 4.48. Josh. 11.3,17. 12.1,5. 13.5,11. Map. 42.6. 89.12? 133.3. Rwiyo 4.8.\x* VaSidhoni vanoritumidza Sirioni\x + Map. 29.6. Det. 4.48.\x*, asi VaAmori vanoritumidza Seniri\x + 1 Makor. 5.23. Rwiyo 4.8.\x*).
\v 10 Maguta ese ebani, neGiriyadhi rose, neBhashani rose\x + 4.43. Josh. 13.9,16,17,21.\x*, kusvika paSareka neEdhirei\x + Josh. 12.5. 13.11.\x*, maguta eushe hwaOgi muBhashani.
\v 11 Nokuti ndiOgi oga mambo weBhashani wakasara pavakasara vevane simba\x + 3.13. 2.11,20. Josh. 12.4. 13.12. Gen. 14.5. Amo. 2.9.\x*; tarira mubhedha wake waiva mubhedha wematare; haupo here paRabha revana vaAmoni\x + 2 Zvak. 11.1. 12.26. Jer. 49.2. Eze. 21.20. 25.5. Amo. 1.14. Josh. 13.25.\x*? Kureba kwawo kwaiva makubhiti mapfumbamwe, neupamhi hwawo hwaiva makubhiti mana, zvichienderana nekubhiti remunhu\x + Zvak. 21.17.\x*.
\v 12 Zvino nyika iyi takaigara nhaka nenguva iyo; kubva paAroeri iri parwizi Arinoni, nehafu yemakomo yeGiriyadhi\x + 2.36.\x*, nemaguta ayo, ndikapa vaRubheni nevaGadhi\x + Num. 32.33. Josh. 12.6. 13.8.\x*.
\v 13 Neyakasara yeGiriyadhi, neBhashani rose, ushe hwaOgi, ndakapa kuhafu yerudzi rwaManase\x + Num. 32.29. Josh. 13.29-31.\x*, dunhu rose reArigobhu, neBhashani rose\x + Det. 3.4,14.\x*, rinotumidzwa nyika yevane simba\x + 3.11.\x*.
\v 14 Jairi mwanakomana waManase wakatora dunhu rose reArigobhu\x + Num. 32.41.\x* kusvika pamuganhu wevaGeshuri nevaMaakati, ndokuitumidza zvichitevera zita rake\x + Josh. 12.5. 13.11,13. 1 Zvak. 27.8. 2 Zvak. 3.3. 10.6. 13.37,38.\x* Bhashani Havhoti-Jairi, kusvika zuva ranhasi\x + Num. 32.41.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino ndakapa Giriyadhi\x + Num. 32.39.\x* kuna Makiri.
\v 16 NekuVaRubheni nekuVaGadhi ndakapa kubva paGiriyadhi kusvikawo parwizi Arinoni, pakati nepakati pemupata, nemuganhu, kusvikawo parwizi Jabhoki\x + 2 Zvak. 24.5.\x*, muganhu wevana vaAmoni\x + Num. 21.24. Josh. 12.2.\x*.
\v 17 Uye mapani, neJoridhani, nemuganhu, kubva paKinereti\x + Num. 34.11.\x*, kusvika kugungwa rebani\x + 4.49.\x*, gungwa remunyu\x + Gen. 14.3.\x*, pajinga peAshidhodhi-Pisiga kumabvazuva.
\p
\v 18 Zvino ndakakurairai nenguva iyo ndichiti: Jehovha Mwari wenyu wakakupai nyika iyi ive nhaka yenyu. Muchayambuka makashonga zvombo pamberi pehama dzenyu, vana vaIsraeri, varume vese vari mhare\x + Num. 32.21.\x*.
\v 19 Koga vakadzi venyu nevanana venyu nezvipfuwo zvenyu, \add nokuti\add* ndinoziva kuti mune zvipfuwo zvizhinji, zvichagara mumaguta enyu andakakupai\x + Num. 32.1,4.\x*.
\v 20 Kusvika Jehovha apa zororo hama dzenyu semwi, naivo vagare nhaka yenyika Jehovha Mwari wenyu yaanovapa mhiri kwaJoridhani\x + Josh. 22.4.\x*; zvino muchadzokera umwe neumwe kunhaka yake yandakakupai.
\p
\v 21 Zvino ndakaraira Joshua panguva iyo ndichiti: Meso ako akaona zvose Jehovha Mwari wenyu zvaakaitira madzimambo awa maviri\x + Num. 27.18.\x*; saizvozvo Jehovha uchaitira ushe hwese kwamunoyambukira.
\v 22 Musavatya, nokuti Jehovha Mwari wenyu iye anokurwirai\x + Eki. 14.14.\x*.
\v 23 Zvino ndakanyengetera kuna Jehovha panguva iyo, ndichiti:
\v 24 Ishe Jehovha, imwi makatanga kuratidza muranda wenyu ukuru hwenyu, neruoko rwenyu rune simba\x + 5.24. 11.2. 32.3. 1 Makor. 29.11.\x*; nokuti ndeupi mwari kumatenga kana panyika angaita zvinoenderana nemabasa enyu, uye zvinoenderana nemasimba enyu\x + Eki. 15.11.\x*?
\v 25 Nditenderei henyu kuyambuka, ndione nyika yakanaka iri mhiri kwaJoridhani, gomo iro rakanaka\x + Eki. 3.8; Det. 4.22.\x*, neRebhanoni\x + Josh. 1.4.\x*.
\v 26 Asi Jehovha wakanditsamwira nekuda kwenyu, akasandinzwa\x + Map. 78.21,59. 89.38. Det. 1.37.\x*; Jehovha ndokuti kwandiri: Zvaringana kwauri! Usachitaurazve kwandiri pamusoro penyaya iyi\x + 2 VaKori. 12.9.\x*.
\v 27 Kwira panhongonya pePisiga\x + Num. 27.12,13.\x*, ugosimudzira meso ako kumavirazuva nekumaodzanyemba nekuchamhembe nekumabvazuva ugoona nemeso ako; nokuti haungayambuki Joridhani urwu.
\v 28 Asi raira Joshua\x + Num. 27.23. Det. 1.38. 31.3,7.\x*, umukurudzire\x + 1.38. 31.7.\x* nekumusimbisa\x + 2.30. 31.7.\x*, nokuti iye uchayambuka pamberi pevanhu ava, uye achavagarisa nhaka yenyika yauchaona\x + 1.38. 31.7.\x*.
\v 29 Zvino takagara pamupata pakatarisana neBheti-Peori\x + 4.46. 34.6.\x*.